{
  "stem": "5470.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had [? liner ?] [? up ?] list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where people had to pay, say, 100 guilders to get on that list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a diamond [INAUDIBLE] that was the diamond list.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was for people who were working in the diamond industry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they paid with diamonds to the Germans to get on that list.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there were several lists.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And yeah, I don't remember all the names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyhow, the Germans were trying to get as much hold of their possessions as possible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If it was in money, if it was in jewelry, or in diamonds, as long as they got hold of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only, only for getting a temporary suspension from transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was only temporary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That all went to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- in the camp, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "SS ?] transport-- people were coming into the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a Jewish bank, Lippmann and Rosenthal, which was, of course, taken over by the Germans too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were collecting all the possession in monies, in jewelry, for people who were arriving with those things in the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, well, what they couldn't hide, well, they lost it to the Lippmann and Roosevelt bank.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After they were registered, they were moved over to the-- this person from Lippmann and Rosenthal bank.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they searched them-- find out anyhow if they were wearing jewelry, rings, and other things, possessions and what they had already in their coats hidden, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- these were Dutch people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think these were from the NSB, the Nazi organization in Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were not too friendly, of course, in handling their business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But people-- most of the people knew already from others who had the experience before, think about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
